{"tid":1795532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偽冒連登官方及會員之名 想食人血饅頭","createTime":"2019-12-24T03:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T04:28:12.000Z","uid":36321,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de08d5da0a7e35c14794be2f2a58fff1f2375146","tid":1795532,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"是咁的 話說呢個so call NBA連登官方gp<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1J0sxU6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1J0sxU6.png&h=743877d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就用榮光 夫子 同 疑似晏慕龍嘅名義搞左個so call Christmas party 原訂今日 一開始就話收錢嘅 同會搵戴祖儀 但俾人chok兩野就改免費 同2打6 同一時間 連登會員夫子更出左澄清 話官方gp入面嘅唔係佢添<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6D535h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6D535h.jpg&h=5e9d9a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/23/224601_e7c714930615a0cbdc11d6a77753a12b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F23%2F224601_e7c714930615a0cbdc11d6a77753a12b.png&h=6e18d9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁唔少人就覺得奇啦 戴祖儀cctvb人唔會冒險出席用榮光做開頭嘅活動 而新請嘅2打6嘉賓都係cctvb訓練班人<br />\n開始有啲懷疑個活動本質係咩呢 於是 就有人私下問左真.晏慕龍啦 點知佢斷言話tg慕龍不是其本人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2135373.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2135373.png&h=4028cb61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁一直就去到今日 正常要搞party嘅日子 假夫子同假慕龍就同時話要順延 到31號先搞 眾gp友群起逼宮 最後一率被禁言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHX6OBS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHX6OBS.png&h=1fb50d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQ2FS4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQ2FS4h.png&h=3f2bf503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6TqgrnH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6TqgrnH.png&h=e86176c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係唔係打算食人血饅頭 同 呃人就閣下自己判斷"}